    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13468#discussion_r3294854299\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>There's no need to add these tests, we don't typically test at this micro-level of granularity. The end-to-end tests are fine. (it becomes extremely onerous to refactor if tests are there for every possible behavior and implementation detail of a function)</p>\n</blockquote>",
